message.body: If you stop home anytime today let me know. I was riding out and think I left the loaf of bread open. I need you to close it up.

Lol ok
How's work been?
It's been good. I like it. Working fulltime makes the days go by so quickly!
How about Uncle #####'s
Do you like it?

Minimum I can make is about 500 extra a month
That's great! I would give you a healthy tip if you delivered my pizza.
Lol.. so when Is the next time I will be seeing you?
We could set a day to hang out
That could work! (Lol you sound like me).. let me know what's good for you and ill work it around my cake orders and oogies schedule.
